release.notes:
Additional Installation Steps: Before ACollab will function properly as a module, the ATutor module.php and ACollab config.inc.php files need to be modified by adding the following lines, adjusting the values accordingly. Include the trailing slash.
		
		Add to ACollab's include/config.inc.php file:
		define('AT_PATH','http://www.mydomain.com/ATutor/');
		define('AT_TABLE_PREFIX','AT_');
		
		Add to ATutor's mods/acollab/module.php
		define('AC_PATH','http://www.mydomain.com/ACollab/');
		define('AC_TABLE_PREFIX','AC_');
